      %h1 
        Bring patients from the web to your waiting room
      %p
        Hopsital and health systems need a steady stream of content to engage patients
        online. Now, you can access a trove of content options - feature stories, patient
        quizzes, illustrations, health news articles, and more - to keep your organization's
        website and e-newsletters fresh. Just select your content, customize it with quotes from
        your own clinicians and information about your organization's services, and publish.
